CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 26, 1957, pg. A17 reads: "Celebrating - Mr. and Mrs. Robert Hand celebrate their 54th wedding anniversary Sunday at Kay Club when Auxiliary Unit No. 2 presented a program which included a special observance of their big day. Here, they cut the handsome anniversary cake. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mr. and Mrs. Robert Hand cutting cake for fifty-fourth wedding anniversary in Kay Boys Club during Kay Women's Auxiliary fashion revue and tea
